s answer questions involving the popular perception of holiness, social class, and gender.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Apr 2021) 0aChristian saintsxCultzEurope. 0aChristianity. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh1 aBell, Rudolph M., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUChP eBook-Package Archive 1960-1989z978311066784440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226890579423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226890579.jpg  a978-3-11-066784-4  UChP eBook-Package Archive 1960-1989c1960d1989  aGBV-deGruyter-alles